### List API keys
GET https://api.gettalko.com/v1/me/api-keys
Authorization: Bearer {{TALKO_API_KEY}}

### Create API key
POST https://api.gettalko.com/v1/me/api-keys
Authorization: Bearer {{TALKO_API_KEY}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Customer backend integration",
  "scopes": ["read", "write"]
}
